I challenge you to find a better slice in town.  Seriously, this is better than the pizza we've had in NY.  The cheese, crust and sauce become one.  The crust is to die for.  When ordering take out, the car is filled with such an amazingly appetizing aroma that I can barely wait to tear open the box as soon as I walk through the door.  Eating in the restaurant is equally pleasurable.  The restaurant is super clean, the staff is very friendly and attentive and the owner is the real deal.  If you love low-key places with awesome food and great service, you should definitely try out Yo Pauly's.  We live 20 miles away...but it is always worth the drive when I'm craving pizza.  The wings are good too!

